{"tid":2201520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"噴鼻式減弱疫苗 潛在臉癱入侵神經同腦部危機?!","createTime":"2020-09-14T00:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T15:52:56.000Z","uid":305261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f27e86f8b5663a4381e2b7379ba8bf3959302c41","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:37:17.000Z","msg":"噴鼻式減活疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 即係隻病毒係仲係在生, 可以複製, 只係弱啲咁解, 所以免疫系統有問題嘅人唔可以打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 要靠群體免疫等病毒喺社區消失; 減活疫苗同小朋友時候已經打咗嘅不活化疫苗唔同, e.g. DTaP- IPV Vaccine: Diphtheria, Tetanus, acellular Pertussis （百日咳) &amp; Inactivated Poliovirus （小兒麻痺症） Vaccine, 不活化疫苗係唔會複製，已死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n噴鼻式疫苗會喺鼻黏膜, 甚至喺口水, 分泌物, 呼吸道, 消化道產生抗體，喺源頭堵截病毒入侵, 亦會產生血液嘅抗體 <br />\n<br />\nIdeal situation原理<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(1) 將減活疫苗噴入鼻腔  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(2) 減活病毒有限度複製  <br />\n(3) Dendritic cells 執到病毒抗原, 再帶去最近嘅黏膜層淋巴組織 <br />\n(4) 呈上俾  na&Iuml;ve T cell, activate 佢 <br />\n(5) 再由CD4+Ｔcell activate B cell 同CD8+Ｔcell <br />\n(6) 不斷繁殖 <br />\n(7) Ｂ cell 再玩一輪DNA排序, 砌出最好嘅抗體,  <br />\n(8)釋放大量抗體(e.g. IgG 入血液, IgA入去鼻黏膜, 呼吸道, 消化道等) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oqw5Rqh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqw5Rqh.png&h=08b4ef08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/319977456_Immune_responses_after_live_attenuated_influenza_vaccination\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F319977456_Immune_responses_after_live_attenuated_influenza_vaccination&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=a5408653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/publication/319977456_Immune_responses_after_live_attenuated_influenza_vaccination</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">但係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n噴鼻式疫苗有安全問題 , 有機會導致臉癱 、腦炎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gWv2TEh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgWv2TEh.png&h=294fa5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鼻腔有嗅神經(olfactory nerve) 連接住中樞神經系統, 減弱嘅病毒都有機會利用retrograde axonal transport經過嗅神經(圖三所顯示)redirect上腦/中樞神經系統 或者積聚喺olfactory bulb同腦組織。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為係噴鼻式，太近腦，所以先會redirect去中樞神經系統，就算唔用減弱病毒，用不活化病毒/淨係得抗原/另一隻病毒都會redirect。好多國家都唔敢輕易批噴鼻式嘅研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，何況係一隻大家都未了解嘅新型病毒。 相反Sublingual(脷底)係唔會redirect，但係都做到鼻黏膜/呼吸道有抗體，點解唔做? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n汁<a href=\"https://www.pnas.org/content/105/5/1644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcontent%2F105%2F5%2F1644&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=01a7b2f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pnas.org/content/105/5/1644</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.06.04.135012v1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biorxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2020.06.04.135012v1&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=1450e997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2020.06.04.135012v1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9yskkb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9yskkb.png&h=1812e446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g6FBX8J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg6FBX8J.png&h=b0a263b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/7943871_Poliovirus_Pathogenesis_of_Poliomyelitis_and_Apoptosis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F7943871_Poliovirus_Pathogenesis_of_Poliomyelitis_and_Apoptosis&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=82920718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.researchgate.net/publication/7943871_Poliovirus_Pathogenesis_of_Poliomyelitis_and_Apoptosis</a><br />\n由右邊尾部走向另一邊，一個駁一個神經細胞入中樞神經系統<br />\n<br />\n已經有研究指出武漢肺炎病毒有入侵神經細胞嘅可能性, 有武漢肺炎病人有腦炎, 喺腦脊髓液亦搵到SARS-CoV-2, 用穿透式電子顯微鏡仲喺額葉腦組織睇到武漢肺炎病毒。而嗅上皮組織(olfactory epithelium)嘅細胞都有俾武漢病毒入侵嘅ACE2 receptor (你當係入細胞嘅一度門)，所以呢隻噴鼻式減弱疫苗係好大機會出事!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n汁<a href=\"https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/jmv.25915\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1002%2Fjmv.25915&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=8a1829b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1002/jmv.25915</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://psychscenehub.com/psychinsights/covid-19-and-the-brain-pathogenesis-and-neuropsychiatric-manifestations-of-sars-cov-2-cns-involvement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpsychscenehub.com%2Fpsychinsights%2Fcovid-19-and-the-brain-pathogenesis-and-neuropsychiatric-manifestations-of-sars-cov-2-cns-involvement%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=19d66061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://psychscenehub.com/psychinsights/covid-19-and-the-brain-pathogenesis-and-neuropsychiatric-manifestations-of-sars-cov-2-cns-involvement/</a> <br />\n<br />\n減弱病毒製作過程<br />\n要將武漢肺炎SARS-CoV-2 嘅致命性/毒性(virulence)減弱, 透過強迫佢喺另一種生物細胞重複, 用佢嘅第n代做疫苗/ 揀隻弱啲, 唔適應人體嘅 mutant strain 做疫苗<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n點解話俄羅斯疫苗嘅數據唔可信, 因為佢搵服緊兵役嘅年輕人去試, 應該搵啲老人渣去試睇下副作用點, 始終隻病毒仲係生, 同埋能唔能夠 activate 免疫系統/產生抗體 (na&iuml;ve T cell 同B cell 嘅數量隨住年齡減少，亦難啲activate)<br />\n<br />\n英國疫苗好似又resume trial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家最後會揀邊隻呢"},{"pid":"16f405f0759e250895ae13c963aaeda2e1cb3c20","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:37:58.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2585e62ce17365710cdd27843be0beb9e343f1e2","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:38:44.000Z","msg":"返工睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867b6e4fc7579c144da226e43c8f7fb62412d5bb","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推呀推呀推呀"},{"pid":"88b0ff8e69696638ec34d445ef4991eaa5367b3c","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:41:52.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f89d9aeaf70ed3dd5cfa274da03def9194859e1","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"677f6e62bfd5946094c2c9a94618a9f5c9142aca","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:44:45.000Z","msg":"諗住靠guilt trip令到我地去檢測?! 你係咪日日驗吖pk"},{"pid":"0ab597684d2cf3dd5041094bc6ad20e3fc863b7d","tid":2201520,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"有冇clinical trial 同 real world study 有呢個rare disease 先？單單係懷疑而冇case 發生過 = 9up, 至少FDA 有冇warning 過？<br />\n<br />\n而家咁同之前果單d 老母唔同仔女打疫苗有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65dc14caf1a3b8c0e30dc1ae78c373eb2eefa940","tid":2201520,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71031aae4fa12eee36a0b68f6fc20aacd43bc09","tid":2201520,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab597684d2cf3dd5041094bc6ad20e3fc863b7d","tid":2201520,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"有冇clinical trial 同 real world study 有呢個rare disease 先？單單係懷疑而冇case 發生過 = 9up, 至少FDA 有冇warning 過？<br />\n<br />\n而家咁同之前果單d 老母唔同仔女打疫苗有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:49:43.000Z","msg":"樓豬張面癱相<br />\n係咪50年前影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c0fbf3358422c673f90b51d01961274ee23c5e","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ab597684d2cf3dd5041094bc6ad20e3fc863b7d","tid":2201520,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:45:44.000Z","msg":"有冇clinical trial 同 real world study 有呢個rare disease 先？單單係懷疑而冇case 發生過 = 9up, 至少FDA 有冇warning 過？<br />\n<br />\n而家咁同之前果單d 老母唔同仔女打疫苗有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14985487/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F14985487%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8KCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=d5aec212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/14985487/</a><br />\n呢個發生之後，intranasal 就好難批<br />\n<br />\n利申: 唔係anti-vaxxer, <br />\n只係覺得有更安全嘅delivery route, 好似sublingual (脷底) 同最常用嘅intramuscular"},{"pid":"ce9f35d00e496d541e3f16cd4d131b42c4fd620a","tid":2201520,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f89d9aeaf70ed3dd5cfa274da03def9194859e1","tid":2201520,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:43:41.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T00:59:33.000Z","msg":"武漢病毒"},{"pid":"1e2ce352661479b